1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,245
If you are wealthy,

2
00:00:01,245 --> 00:00:05,493
understand that it has been given to you so that
you can give it to those who are less so.

3
00:00:05,493 --> 00:00:08,772
If you are smart, then use it to serve.

4
00:00:08,772 --> 00:00:13,032
Look at people in society who are much
less smart than you,

5
00:00:13,032 --> 00:00:16,120
who can't work things out for themselves.

6
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:21,418
Stand up so that you can be the strength to
others who can't stand up on their own two feet.

7
00:00:21,418 --> 00:00:24,337
And then they will hold on to you when you
stand,

8
00:00:24,337 --> 00:00:29,235
because they just don't have the courage,
the guts to stand up on their own.

9
00:00:29,235 --> 00:00:32,482
They'll want you, they'll need you to
carry them forward.

10
00:00:32,482 --> 00:00:35,521
And don't stop, because if you stop,
they'll all stop.

11
00:00:35,521 --> 00:00:38,337
There are those who look up to you for
inspiration.

12
00:00:38,337 --> 00:00:45,311
There are those who are still alive because they
look at you and they feel like life is living.

13
00:00:45,311 --> 00:00:47,418
Sometimes you don't even know these
things.

14
00:00:47,418 --> 00:00:49,743
know, if you can become someone like that,

15
00:00:49,743 --> 00:00:52,317
that's really a life worth having lived.

16
00:00:52,317 --> 00:00:54,728
These are the greatest ambitions in life.

17
00:00:54,728 --> 00:01:00,250
If you can live to give life to others,
that's a great life, isn't it?
